  "content": "<p>This year we had three intrepid players representing the Edmonton Squash Club at the always fun 2018 Northwest Territories Territorial Squash Championships.</p>\n<p>Mohammed Elserafy competed in Men&#8217;s B, finishing second.</p>\n<p>John Clarkin played in the Open division and was runner-up.</p>\n<p>Ibrahim Elserafy played in the Exhibition draw that included the 2017 Canadian National Champion and came 3rd.</p>\n<p>Thank you to Melina Turk for organizing such a great event again, and to the <a href=\"https://ykracquetclub.com/\">Yellowknife Racquet Club</a> for hosting.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><div id='gallery-2' class='gallery galleryid-3574 gallery-columns-2 gallery-size-large'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/2018-northwest-territories-territorial-squash-championships/yellowknife-1/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"778\" height=\"778\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-1.jpg 778w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-1-20x20.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 778px) 100vw, 778px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/2018-northwest-territories-territorial-squash-championships/yellowknife-2/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"778\" height=\"778\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-2.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-2.jpg 778w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-2-300x300.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-2-20x20.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 778px) 100vw, 778px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/2018-northwest-territories-territorial-squash-championships/yellowknife-3/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"778\" height=\"778\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-3.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-3.jpg 778w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-3-150x150.jpg 150w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-3-300x300.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-3-20x20.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 778px) 100vw, 778px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/2018-northwest-territories-territorial-squash-championships/yellowknife-4/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"778\" height=\"778\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-4.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-4.jpg 778w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-4-150x150.jpg 150w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-4-300x300.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Yellowknife-4-20x20.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 778px) 100vw, 778px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure>\n\t\t</div>\n</p>\n",
